                        <note rend="inline" type="source">625.116/25: Telegram</note>
                        <head><hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to
                                the Chargé in Chile</hi> (<persName type="to"><hi rend="italic">Scott</hi></persName>)</head>
                        <opener>
                            <dateline rendition="#right"><placeName><hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi></placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1935-08-13T19:00:00-04:00">August 13, 1935—7
                                p.m.</date></dateline>
                        </opener>
                        <p>49. Embassy’s despatch 423 of July 31, 1935. You are authorized in your
                            discretion to present to the Foreign Office the note enclosed in the
                            above-mentioned despatch.</p>
                        <closer><signed><hi rend="smallcaps">Hull</hi></signed></closer>
